Text: Hi Beebe85, I just want you to know that although I am a long time user of thepiratebay.org, I registered in it only today, so that I can write a big "Thank you" for your KUNG FU series offer.

As far as this help is concerned, you can count me in for sure:-) The least I can do for you!
